Version 1.0.5.20140212 Info
February 12, 2014
Released under Mozilla Public License, version 2.0 About this Add-on
Slimming the Australis Theme of Firefox 28This add-on features all below optional appearance alterationsToolbar over Navbar Makes the Personal Toolbar appear over the Navigation bar.Compress Bookmark Toolbar Gives you some more space for your bookmarks.Autohide Navbar The Navigation Bar will only be visible when the mouse is over the Bookmarks and Tabs area, as well as when writing an url or using the searchbar.Tabs always in Titlebar Move the tabs into the title bars when having restored(non-fullscreen) windows.Compress Navbar Items Should make the Navigation bar slimmer when having custom icons in it. (Add-ons could override this with their own style)Issue reporting and feature requestsSubmit those here: Australis Slimmr Github Issue TrackerSource CodeIs available at The Australis Slimmr Github Page.DonationsIf you would like to promote the development of this add-on and future add-ons you can donate using the following methodsBitcoin 1E8Rfg6teXpvijmiiB8LiRJAukpSbXtAbhPayPalFlattr
